text:
<Niha house terrace .. She is folding the clothes..>

Hero : Baledu.. Em set avvatle..
Niha : Nuvvu emi tharun bhascker oo trivikram oo kadhu , ippude start chestunnav kadha.. alane untadhi
Hero : konchem aina confidence undali kadha .
Niha : Em parled , ivanni chepukodaniki baguntay .. taruvatha press conference lona , Arjun gurinchi cheppandi ani naku mike icchinappudu â€¦
Hero : oooooooo aaagu , antha dooram vellaku ..
<both laughs together >
Niha : Shwetha ela undhi..
Arjun : still laughing .. nods his head .
Niha : Mari Maya?
Arjun : Tanake.. chala bagundhi ..
Niha : Repu edho plan chestunnav anta,aman cheppadu
Arjun : Tana Bday repu
Niha : aythe plan ee night kadha cheyyali
Arjun : Tanu puttina time 4 in evening anta, paiga hasta rendava padam , mana mrugasira tho manchi communication undhi. ikkada makaram akkada midhunam.
             deadly idhi
Niha : LAUGHS , velli jathakalu chepko , thanaki telusa mari bday kosam pilichav ani 
Arjun : Surprise ani cheppa
Niha : Yemyndra mee abbalaki , thana bday roju surprise ante aa matram teledha aa ammyiki.. Burra vaadandi ra, Abaddham aadadam tappu kadhu aadi dorikipovadam 
            Tappu , abaddham aadithe atukunnatu undali.. 
Arjun : Mee daggara chala nerchukovali guruji..
Niha : Na saktulu anni daara postunna , viccahla vidiga vaadesko.
< Small chatter>
